<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>마인크래프트 4종 체험</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 헤더 추가 -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center multicolor-text">마인크래프트 4종 체험</h1>
        <p class="text-center">다양한 마인크래프트 활동을 통해 코딩을 배우고 창의력을 발휘해보세요!</p>
        <div class="row">
            <!-- 카드 1: 마인크래프트 보야지 아쿠아틱 -->
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='//studio.code.org/s/aquatic/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-img-box">
                        <img src="/images/mc/minecraft-activity-aquatic.png" class="card-img-top" alt="보야지 아쿠아틱">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-text-box">
                        <h5 class="card-title">보야지 아쿠아틱</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">수중 세계를 탐험하며 문제 해결 능력을 발휘해보세요.</p>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/aquatic/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/aquatic" class="btn btn-secondary">수업 계획 보기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 카드 2: 마인크래프트 히어로의 여정 -->
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='//studio.code.org/s/hero/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-img-box">
                        <img src="/images/mc/minecraft-activity-journey.png" class="card-img-top" alt="히어로의 여정">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-text-box">
                        <h5 class="card-title">히어로의 여정</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">에이전트에게 명령을 내리고 장애물을 극복하세요.</p>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/hero/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/hero" class="btn btn-secondary">수업 계획 보기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 카드 3: 마인크래프트 어드벤처러 -->
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='//studio.code.org/s/mc/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-img-box">
                        <img src="/images/mc/minecraft-activity-adventurer.png" class="card-img-top" alt="어드벤처러">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-text-box">
                        <h5 class="card-title">어드벤처러</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">코드를 작성해 마인크래프트 세계를 탐험하세요.</p>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/mc/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/mc" class="btn btn-secondary">수업 계획 보기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 카드 4: 마인크래프트 디자이너 -->
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='//studio.code.org/s/minecraft/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-img-box">
                        <img src="/images/mc/minecraft-activity-designer.png" class="card-img-top" alt="디자이너">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-text-box">
                        <h5 class="card-title">디자이너</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">기본 코딩을 배우고 자신만의 마인크래프트 게임을 만드세요.</p>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/minecraft/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                        <a href="//studio.code.org/s/minecraft" class="btn btn-secondary">수업 계획 보기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/header.js"></script> <!-- header.js 로드 -->
</body>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</html>
